   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">There are multiple customer service offers that can be ordered
when required. The following sections gives an overview of the different
services.</p>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Customer Training</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Depending
on the level and type of training needed there are standard courses
or customized courses available.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">The standard courses provide
general theoretical knowledge about Reality systems. The project specific
courses provide both practical and theoretical knowledge for your
customized system.</p>
